item.title: CVE-2023-34412|2023-11-16T11:02:33.346Z -- red%20lion%20europe -- mbnet
item.description: A vulnerability in Red Lion Europe mbNET/mbNET.rokey and Helmholz REX 200 and REX 250 devices with firmware lower 7.3.2 allows an authenticated remote attacker with high privileges to inject malicious HTML or JavaScript code (XSS).
